Manually renaming it did not work for me.

sudo pip3 install ./tensorflow-0.8.0-cp35-none-linux_x86_64.whl

Gave me the same error:
tensorflow-0.8.0-cp35-none-linux_x86_64.whl is not a supported wheel on this platform.

On Ubuntu 16.04

Anything else that you did?
